Package cz.dawon.java.gui.parserSetup.cards

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICard
    Interface representating one "page" in setup wizard
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCard
    Abstract implementation for ICard
    AbstractSelectNodeCard
    Abstract card for selecting nodes
    ExportCard
    Lets user export settings to file
    ImportCard
    Lets user select whether to setup parser manually or from file
    JGraphAnalysisSettings
    Class storing all data between all cards in wizard - no need to use getters and setters, this class will be used just in the wizard and all the checks are made in wizard.
    SelectActionCard
    Allows user to select Node representing Action
    SelectActionIdCard
    Allows user to select Attribute or Node representing Action ID
    SelectFileCard
    Allows user to select single file to be parsed
    SelectFolderCard
    Allows user to select folder to be looked in
    SelectModeCard
    First card allowing user to select whether to parse single file or folder with multiple files
    SelectNodeCard
    Allows user to select Attribute or Node representing Action Data, (Tight) Prerequisity and (Tight) Follower
    UniversalFileFilter
    Universal file filter
    XMLMutableTreeNode
    Modified DefaultMutableTreeNode to be used with Node
    XMLTreeCellRenderer
    Custom style for JTree items
